title: Micro Pressure - EDM Tonal Kicks MULTiFORMAT
description:
[img]http://geo-media.beatport.com/image_size/500x500/10776454.jpg[/img]

Hy2rogen dives into the new year with the first release featuring 120 key labelled speaker punishing EDM kicks.

One of the most important elements of this type of music is the kick drum.

Taking inspiration from the current musical trend, drum maestro Hy2rogen cooks up a fresh batch of kicks to be added to your personal library of production weaponry.

Going from light distortion/fuzzy kicks to basic edm wombers with a strong attack, all of the kicks have been maxed out and key labelled, perfect for that drag & drop action.

All of the sounds are offered as 24bit WAV files.

Don't let the demo fool you, there's much more inside! 

Specifications:

120 key labelled EDM kicks
synths, effects and other elements that can be heard in the demo are not included in the pack!
